Attribution

This specification is the cross-platform generalization of the manifest
pattern first shipped by AgentMindCloud/grok-install (v2.14), also by
Jani Solo. grok-install remains the Grok-specific form of the same
idea; universal-spawn is the cross-platform superset.

See:
  - https://github.com/AgentMindCloud/grok-install
  - docs/grok-compat.md in this repository

